description: The Reality TV Podcast discusses all the latest happenings in the world Reality TV, including recaps and commentary of shows like Survivor, The Amazing Race, Big Brother, American Idol, The Mole, The Apprentice, Project Runway & other Reality Television shows that are on air right now. Plus, interviews with your favorite Reality TV Stars, the day after they are kicked off their show!!
